Blue Skies R E & Resort Rental

data.description: Gorgeous home in a sweet area of Big Bear City called Shay Meadows with views of the mountains out your back door. This wonderful home offers plenty of space for everyone with 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, a living room with a beautiful fireplace to cozy up to, plus a family room/game room that has a wood burning stove! Beautiful entryway, formal dining room off the stunning kitchen, plus another dining area open to the kitchen, laundry room and a full bath downstairs. Master suite, 3 more bedrooms, and a full bath upstairs. Attached, oversized 2 car garage with plenty of storage, all on a huge, fully fenced, nicely treed, level lot! Wow! Room for all of your cars, boat, RV, toys, etc.! Dogs will love this yard! This home was completed in 2005 by the current owners and only used as a second home. Furnishings are negotiable too! Easy access from Hwy 38 and only minutes to the ski slopes, lake and Village! At only $274/ sq ft, you won't want to miss this one. It's a fantastic home!
